title: BONUS - A Grain of Truth from The Witcher
description:
An episode from Aziz's side podcast project on The Witcher. This one corresponds to the first episode of Season 2 of The Witcher on Netflix.

If you enjoy, check out the rest of the Podcast of Surprise: https://anchor.fm/azizahai or https://open.spotify.com/show/6TD962j0qnDBgVvN03RQFK
